 「性贿赂」之外，更多的是金钱贿赂。在近些年互联网大厂通报的腐败事件中，更多的也是此类。以阿里为例，最著名的属前聚划算总经理阎利珉受贿案。因为在聚划算工作期间，先后两次收受贿赂，总计价值 53.8 万余元，阎利珉被判刑 7 年。 焦点分析｜阿里女员工被侵犯，零售业何以成为性贿赂和腐败重灾区？_详细解读_最新资讯_热点事件_36氪"},"attached_info":"Cj8IlMG1h4W01ZMUEAMaCDY4NjU4NzgxIOW0yIgGMCU4pghAD3IJNDc4Njk5Njg0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"279 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-5ebdb1b33a4ad9e431123ff8df53dd0e_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"16_1628679958.83085","card_id":"Q_478811156","target":{"id":478811156,"title":"如何评价 8 月 10 日小米正式推出的 MIUI 12.5 增强版？有哪些新的功能？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/478811156","type":"question","created":1628602825,"answer_count":77,"follower_count":218,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[488,890,6119,25405,691069],"comment_count":15,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"8 月 10 日小米发布了 MIUI 12.5 的全新稳定版（增强版），实际使用下的体验如何？ 比较奇怪的是完全没提动画和功能增减，似乎这些是一定要保留的。"},"attached_info":"Cj8IlMG1h4W01ZMUEAMaCDY4NjgzNjU3IMmDyogGMA842gFAEHIJNDc4ODExMTU2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"276 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-5ba9e1439231f1a211bdf33b88e911e6_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"17_1628679958.8313344","card_id":"Q_478409760","target":{"id":478409760,"title":"年轻人有多反感酒局文化？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/478409760","type":"question","created":1628487769,"answer_count":179,"follower_count":388,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[454,28402,38154,77583,165719],"comment_count":12,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"近日，阿里女员工酒后被侵犯事件引发关注，阿里支持员工拒绝陪酒。有网友表示，职场中因为担心被穿小鞋，不敢拒绝领导的陪酒要求，但内心里极度抵触酒局文化。你认为，年轻人有多反感酒局文化？"},"attached_info":"Cj8IlMG1h4